In re Resignation of Palmer.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Palmer (1996), 75 Ohio St.3d 1201.]

(No. 96-232 Submitted February 21, 1996 Decided March 6, 1996.)

The resignation as an attorney of Jack Harold Palmer of Defiance, Ohio, Attorney Registration No. 0010089, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
